high_descs: Turn around, hang a left at the sink and turn left at the wall to face the white table.
Pick up the far right head of lettuce on the table.
Turn left and walk to the fridge on your left.
Put the head of lettuce inside the fridge on the middle shelf, chill it for seven seconds, remove it and close the door.
Turn around and walk to the white table on your right.
Put the chilled head of lettuce to the left of the coffee maker near the knife with the yellow handle on the table.
anns.task_desc: Place a chilled head of lettuce on a table.

high_descs: Turn around to your right,walk straight, turn left and stand on the right side of the table
Pick up the cabbage on your right at the table
Turn left walk straight turn left facing the fridge
Open the fridge chill the cabbage in, take it out then close the fridge
Turn left walk forward turn right face the table
Put the cabbage on the right side of the table
anns.task_desc: Put the chilled cabbage on the table

high_descs: move to fridge to the left of the stove
pick up lettuce from the table
move to the fridge behind you
chill the lettuce in the fridge for a moment
move to the table to the left of you
put the lettuce on the table
anns.task_desc: Put chilled lettuce on a table.
